  - The compiler error path shows src/main/java/com/java_template/application/processor/CheckCompleteCriterion.java (processor folder).
  - Meanwhile the correct criterion implementation lives under src/main/java/com/java_template/application/criterion/CheckCompleteCriterion.java and has been updated to use ObjectNode.
- The processor package contains a stale copy that still expects Map<String,Integer> for Job.getResultSummary() (old Job type). That file conflicts with the entity type changes (Job now uses ObjectNode for resultSummary).

